  To use Firebase App Hosting and Cloud Storage for Firebase, your Firebase project needs to be on the [pay-as-you go (Blaze) pricing plan](https://firebase.google.com/docs/projects/billing/firebase-pricing-plans#blaze-pricing-plan), which means it's linked to a [Cloud Billing account](https://firebase.google.com/docs/projects/billing/firebase-pricing-plans#cloud-billing-accounts).
  
